OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOn board with an airman    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffighting Ukraine's war in  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fthe sky                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The best way to come back alive is to  
OL,6, stay low, hugging the ground, and      
OL,7, skimming the treetops. Too low and you 
OL,8, can be shot down by machine gun fire - 
OL,9, too high and you can be detected by    
OL,10, enemy air defence systems.             
OL,12,FFor helicopter pilots in war-time      
OL,13,FUkraine, there is little margin for    
OL,14,Ferror.                                 
OL,16,FJust ask Roman.                        
OL,18,FHe has flown countless combat missions 
OL,19,Ffor Ukraine's Sikorsky Brigade and been
OL,20,Fdecorated for valour. He tells us his  
OL,21,Fage - 34 - but not his last name.      
